Package: rAMOPLS
Title: rAMOPLS: Perform ANOVA-Multiblock Orthogonal Partial Least Square Analysis
Version: 1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Sylvain", "Dechaumet", email = "sylvain.dechaumet@medday-pharma.com", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Julien", "Boccard", email = "Julien.Boccard@unige.ch", role = c("aut", "rev")),
    person("Baptiste", "Jolivet", email = "baptiste.jolivet@mines-paristech.fr", role = c("aut", "ctr")))
Description: A tool to perform AMOPLS analysis as described by Boccard et al., 2016 with balanced and unbalanced groups using the subsampling strategy described by Gonzalez et al., 2017.
